{"tid":56940,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"刺蝟的故事","createTime":"2016-12-27T15:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T15:57:54.000Z","uid":59670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80c5f97cc9308ea75cac3b79aad6ee193335d242","tid":56940,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"一個寒冷的冬天，幾隻刺猬擠在一起取暖。由於牠們身上長滿了短刺，彼此戳痛了對方，所以不得不散開。可是，寒冷的天氣又驅使牠們擠在一起，同樣的事情重複發生。牠們終於明白：不要太近，也不要太遠，最好彼此保持一定的距離。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e15842a380273898d05ff356bf8fae41d2f72e","tid":56940,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"人越大越難同人交心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fd4026dc3aafd1bdf386c5598fa4db105293e9","tid":56940,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"我個ex都比我睇過呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fd5a0f5788b88bf100e522a546ad7b10e61ed3","tid":56940,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"刺蝟冇左刺係咪叫做:  喂！？"},{"pid":"654d1b3eafd3d5c294819d25d85227c8980a0d43","tid":56940,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>刺蝟冇左刺係咪叫做:  喂！？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好笑喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795eb3f756c0ae2ab9c5d8d5e66478356df681ca","tid":56940,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"Dse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}